Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}對著神質問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我並非獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:52.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身邊 對我伸出這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}沒什麼好害怕的
